PrecisAmendment to the ONTARIO FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1989 modifying references to the various sport fishing licences, introducing the concept of conservation licences, restricting the use of stringers or live baskets on certain lakes, banning the possession of ruffe (fish species), and providing for fishery observers to board commercial fishing vessels to collect biological information.

Attachments
precis:
Amendment to the ONTARIO FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1989 modifying references to
the various sport fishing licences, introducing the concept of conservation
licences, restricting the use of stringers or live baskets on certain
lakes, banning the possession of ruffe (fish species), and providing for
fishery observers to board commercial fishing vessels to collect
biological information.
